<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt text-xs ms-1"></i></a></div></div></div></div></section><div class="container-fluid"><div class="row mt-5 mb-5"><div class="col-lg-8 col-sm-6 col-11 mx-auto"><h3 class="title text-secondary">Latest Writing</h3><div class="row"><div class="col-lg-6 justify-content-center d-flex flex-column"><div class="card"><div class="d-block blur-shadow-image"><a href="https://brunoamaral.eu/story/week/week-01/"><img src="/story/week/week-01/images/marcel-eberle-rendLSpkDtY-unsplash_hu3d03a01dcc18bc5be0e67db3d8d209a6_3324241_800x533_fill_q85_lanczos_smart1.jpg" alt="img-blur-shadow-blog-2" class="img-fluid border-radius-lg" loading="lazy"></a></div><div class="colored-shadow" style="background-image:url(/story/week/week-01/images/marcel-eberle-rendLSpkDtY-unsplash_hu3d03a01dcc18bc5be0e67db3d8d209a6_3324241_800x533_fill_q85_lanczos_smart1.jpg)"></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-6 justify-content-center d-flex flex-column pl-lg-5 pt-lg-0 pt-3"><div class="category text-primary mt-3 h6">Weekly Journal</div><h3 class="card-title"><a href="https://brunoamaral.eu/story/week/week-01/" class="text-dark">Week 01</a></h3><p class="card-description">The first week of 2024 is past and we&rsquo;re all focused on our goals, and on improving our well-being in some way. So I am going to give you an idea that you can implement right now and turn into a healthy habit.
Open your calendar and write a note to yourself in the future. One month, two, three, whatever makes sense to you. I do that whenever I am going through a rough patch, when I want to remember the day I met someone special when I want to see how one of my decisions turned out. <a href="https://brunoamaral.eu/story/week/week-01/" class="text-darker icon-move-right text-sm"><br>Read more
